<p class="">If eventually things had turned out differently, the position would have been different altogether.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a57c4ea7-7ee7-4d9b-b6e9-541d3b179069" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
