<p class="">I know that in Bordeaux we had about one room in an hotel as the Embassy, and I also know the assistance the Royal Navy gave, with my personal observation on the spot, in carrying the traffic at that time. The comment of the hon. Member shows the kind of statement which can be made—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
