                Mr. Gallacher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-437d6edb-d5a7-4dbd-a5d1-a24e691a6236" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
