    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Can the hon. Gentleman give us his view, from his experience in the Far East, which we all <span id="1277" class="column-number" data-column-number="1277"></span> respect, as to whether it is possible to hold Hong Kong in the face of a hostile China?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3ef57224-5156-4713-9ea9-d17beb38e441" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-05-05/debates/5c53f9bb-07a6-4ce4-a682-2b358370f699/China(BritishPolicy)#contribution-3ef57224-5156-4713-9ea9-d17beb38e441">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-6390c131-35db-4343-b477-9a0f02b92744">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-6390c131-35db-4343-b477-9a0f02b92744">
