<p class="">We have had a very interesting Debate. I must say that I preferred the more measured words of the right hon. Member for Saffron Walden (Mr. R. A. Butler) to the rather portentous opening of the <span id="1342" class="column-number" data-column-number="1342"></span> right hon. Member for Bromley (Mr. H. Macmillan).</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
